reviewText:
Interesting application of lean concepts to dentistry.
Inspired changes in established dental practice routine.

I've been fortunate to visit the Bahri Dental Group and I've seen first hand how they have an amazing culture. This video brings their gemba to you in an engaging and informative video. As the video shows, quality is defined by happy customers (patients) and happy engaged staff. This video is a must see - not just for dentists or other healthcare professionals, but for all who are working on a Lean journey.
